nodes.text: Quinze was serving a term as one of the Peacekeepers in 22 ABY. As such, Quinze enforced the laws of the Outbound Flight Colony, the government established by those who survived the Galactic Republic's extra-galactic survey ship Outbound Flight after it crashed in a star cluster called the Redoubt. Quinze was assigned to guard the Quarantine section, where the colony kept Force-sensitive children under surveillance, alongside Perry.
Quinze was briefly mentioned in the 2004 novel Survivor's Quest, written by Timothy Zahn.
